Package: proto_epi
Title: SEIR Epidemiological Modelling Prototype
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Cristian", "Paez", email = "paez.cristian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Modular Shiny prototype for interactive SEIR epidemiological
    modelling, developed as part of the Pandemic Preparedness Toolkit
    (Argentina Unit), funded by Wellcome. Supports scenario simulation,
    parameter adjustment, healthcare resource pressure analysis, and
    CSV export of results.
